snippet.title: HIND - The Russian Combat Helicopter Simulation gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for HIND - The Russian Combat Helicopter Simulation, Dos PC game produced by Interactive Magic in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/hind-the-russian-combat-helicopter-simulation/4913/
HIND - The Russian Combat Helicopter Simulation is a very interesting game, as it's name suggests, a helicopter simulator very nice and well done. It is an action game with many interesting missions.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
